title: Paris Hilton by Paris Hilton for Women - 1.7 Ounce EDP Spray
description: Paris Hilton by Paris Hilton for Women - 1.7 oz EDP SprayWhen applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied
